Adding an Add to Cart Button to Collection Pages in Shopify Debut Theme Ajax
<!-- slug -->
adding-an-add-to-cart-button-to-collection-pages-in-debut-theme-ajax
<!-- meta title -->
Adding Add to Cart Button to Shopify Debut Theme Collection Pages Ajax
<!-- meta description -->
Shopify Debut theme comes with Ajax facility already. This means, when you add an item to the cart, the page does not refresh or take you to the cart page as many other Shopify themes do. Instead, the item gets added into the cart at the backend while you remain on the same page and you get a notification.
